    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine Domini. Anno ab incarnatione Domini millesimo centesimo septimo,
                        die qu[a]rto mensis iulii, indictione quintadecima, <placeName
                            ref="#places/594">Ravenne</placeName>. Quia peto a vobis domino
                            <persName key="#Monks"><name ref="Iohannes Pomposianus"
                            >Iohanne</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Monks">monacho</rs>
                        <rs key="#Monasteries">monasterii</rs>
                        <orgName
                            key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis #Rivers #Landed_possessions #Monasteries"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/1460">Sancte Marie in <placeName
                                ref="#places/4179">Ponposea</placeName></orgName>, ad confirmandam a
                        domino <persName key="#Abbots" ref="#people/4305">Alberto</persName>
                        <rs key="#Abbots">abbate</rs> iamdicti monasterii et cum consensu
                        monachorum, uti michi presenti in Christi nomine <persName><name
                                ref="Rodulfus de Iohanne de Walterio">Redulfo de Iohanne de
                                Gualterio</name></persName> seu filiis et nepotibus meis, per <rs
                            key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis">enfiteuticarium ius</rs> a presenti
                        die concedistis nobis rem iuris vestri monasterii, idest unum <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions">spacium terre</rs> supra <rs key="#Rivers"
                            >fluvium</rs>
                        <placeName
                            key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis #Confinia #Rivers #Landed_possessions"
                            ref="#places/3558">Teguriensem</placeName>: a primo <rs key="#Confinia"
                            >latere</rs> posidet <persName key="#Confinia"><name
                                ref="Petrus de Walterio">Petrus de Gualterio</name></persName>
                        frater meus iure vestri monasterii, a secundo latere <rs key="#Walls"
                            >muro</rs> civitatis, a tercio <persName key="#Confinia"><name
                                ref="Ebbo">Eppo</name></persName> vestro iure atque a quarto latere
                        predicto fluvio. Et insuper concedistis mihi petitori unum alium spacium
                        terre quod emi a <persName key="#Landed_possessions"><name
                                ref="Carbuncellus">Carboncello</name></persName> de <persName><name
                                ref="Iohannes de Carbone">Iohanne de Carbone</name></persName>: a
                        primo latere posidet <persName key="#Confinia"><name ref="Marnellus"
                                >Marnellus</name></persName> vestro iure, a secundo latere predicto
                        muro, a tercio <persName key="#Confinia"><name ref="Mangragnolus"
                                >Mangagnolo</name></persName> vestro iure atque a quarto latere iam
                        dicto fluvio. Et similiter concedistis mihi iamdicto petitori meisque filiis
                        et nepotibus unum spacium terre iuxta gatulum <orgName key="#Monasteries"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/1477">Sancti Zacharie</orgName>: a primo latere
                        via iamdicti gatuli, a secundo latere iamdicto muro, a tercio
                                <persName><name ref="Mincignanus">Mincignano</name></persName> iure
                        vestri monasterii atque a quarto latere prenominato fluvio. Habenda,
                        tenenda, posidenda predicta spacia et in omnibus melioranda, sub pensione
                        quam vobis et vestris successoribus dare debeamus pro iamdictis spaciis
                        terre, omni marcio mense aut infra indictionem, <rs key="#Rent_in_money">sex
                            denarios tantum monete Venecie</rs>. Pro eo quia exinde accepistis,
                        calciarii nomine, denariorum Veneticorum libras decem. Ita et post transitum
                        meum suprascriptis petitoris meorumque filiorum et nepotum, munimine
                        expleto, tunc predicta spacia terre meliorata ad ius vestri monasterii modis
                        omnibus revertantur, sub poene nomine <rs key="#Penalty">auri duarum
                            unciarum</rs>, et soluta poena maneat firma hec peticio enfiteosis.</ab>
